<div class="about-container">
  <h1>About Campus MarketPlace</h1>

  <p>
    Campus MarketPlace is a student-focused platform that makes it easier for students
    at Ontario Tech to buy, sell, or trade items safely on campus.
  </p>

  <h2>Our Mission</h2>
  <p>
    Our goal is to create a trusted, student-driven community where unused items can
    find new owners. This helps students save money, reduce waste, and support each
    other.
  </p>

